20:55.354 --> 21:02.194 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
She also said that these
programs were the
subject of multiple debates in
media, in newspapers,

21:02.228 --> 21:03.996 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
