articles from newspapers about
drone strikes.

21:08.767 --> 21:11.737 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, she thought it was OK to
write about that.

21:11.770 --> 21:16.175 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: At one point,
