of NPR joining us, thanks so
much.

22:27.279 --> 22:34.019 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
CARRIE JOHNSON: Thank you.

22:34.053 --> 22:43.162 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: But, first:
