25:08.941 --> 25:10.175 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WILLIAM C. RHODEN: Right.

25:10.209 --> 25:12.378 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: We're quick to
